  "created": "2026-03-16",
  "description": "Echolocation as spatial awareness — the orca mapping the size of its world. echoReso sits at 0.7, resonance already audible, comb filtering colouring every note. Mod wheel sweeps resonance from 0.4 to 0.95, approaching self-oscillation — the space getting smaller as reflections multiply, walls closing in. At maximum wheel the territory becomes a corridor of pure resonant tone. Aftertouch damps the echo suddenly, a safety valve — the space snapping open again. Velocity opens filterCutoff, soft touches exploring the darker registers of the water column, hard strikes piercing through toward the surface.",
